label.text: Exchangeability New Part X - New parts may be used on old models as they are
Exchangeability New Part Y - New parts may be used on old models in combination with other parts
Exchangeability New Part Z - New parts must not be used on old models
Exchangeability Old Part 1 - Old parts may be used on new models as they are
Exchangeability Old Part 2 - Old parts may be used on new models in combination with other parts
Exchangeability Old Part 3 - Old parts must not be used on new models
Exchangeability Old Part 4 - Old parts must not be used either on old models or new models

Solution Items are the new revisions or new parts that are to be released by this change.
